Package semsim.annotation

Interface Relation

All Known Implementing Classes:
CurationalMetadata.Metadata, SemSimRelations.SemSimRelation, SemSimRelations.StructuralRelation
public interface Relation
Interface that provides methods for getting information about relations (AKA predicates, AKA qualifiers) used in annotations.
